caption.text: Impress yourself, don't let anyone judge you for who you are...

It doesn't matter what people think about you, it's what you think about yourself that really matters...
A new year is on the way and the possibilities are endless, till we meet again...
Stop hating yourself for everything you aren't and start loving yourself for everything you already are...
Rules are for people who doesn't know what to do...

Whatever you love could be taken away, so live like it's your dying day...
